metadata.name: Bloom in full moon
metadata.description: "Bloom in Full Moon" is an exquisite artwork by the talented artist Kartikey, inspired by the intricate designs of Mechanicles, the antagonist from Aladdin TV series. With his skilled use of color, composition, and technique, Kartikey has brought to life the mechanical insect-inspired elements in a unique and captivating way. Fun Trivia - Kartikey loves talking about himself in third person.
